txt.en: After exploring Mur Shatraug, the Witch-gate, you have discovered Dourhands loyal to the Iron Crown guarding the pass to Câr Bronach. Countless supplies are scattered among their encampment on the Witch-gate, many of which are still bound and sealed to resist the harsh clime of Câr Bronach. Though wicked, the Dourhands are not overfond of Orkish rations or weapon-craft, so it is likely their supplies might contain things of value to the Gabil'akkâ as they work to reclaim Mount Gundabad.\n\nYou should collect Dourhand supply-crates at Mur Shatraug for the good of the Gabil'akkâ.
Collect Dourhand supply-crates at Mur Shatraug
Encamped at Mur Shatraug, the Witch-gate, the Dourhands loyal to the Iron Crown dutifully guard the pass to Câr Bronach.
Mur Shatraug: Supplies for the Gabil'akkâ

You have collected many supply-crates at Mur Shatraug, depriving the Dourhands loyal to the Iron Crown of vital resources. These supply-crates will be searched and their contents will be used to aid the Gabil'akkâ in the reclamation of Mount Gundabad.
